➜【行情分析】比特币加速冲高，要警惕突然下跌
http://www.sohu.com/a/427840129_100217347	16307
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201028/ff101b995e7946f8b30890d49014b57d.png" width="793" height="3212" /></p>
